Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/natural_gift">Natural Gift</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/natural_gift">Natural Gift</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>The user draws power to attack by using its held Berry. The Berry determines its type and power.</p>